FBIS4-29129 "dreas116_i_94006" FBIS-EAS-94-116 Daily Report 5 Jun 1994 Cambodia Commission To Monitor Vietnamese Formed Commission To Monitor Vietnamese Formed BK1606054294 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 5 Jun 94 BK1606054294 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia Cambodian BFN [Statement by "1,150 Cambodian intellectuals, professors, and students" dated 8 June -- read by announcer] [Excerpt] "We, 1,150 intellectuals, professors, and students in Phnom Penh would like to announce the establishment of the Provisional National Commission to check Vietnamese nationals who are spreading throughout and annexing Cambodian territory, and appeal to all compatriots to join this commission in great numbers so that we can examine the issue of the Vietnamese aggressors and discuss further measures to solve the problem." [Passage omitted reviewing movement of Vietnamese nationals into Cambodia and blaming Vietnam and its surrogates for creating this problem]
